			<digest>
				Mousing activity can be reported to the UI and the Outlet
			</digest>
			<description>
				Mousing behaviour is entirely dependent on the settings of the <m>mousemode</m> and <m>mousecurve</m> and <m>freqstyle</m> attributes. <br />
				If the <m>mousemode</m> attribute <b>== 1</b> or <b>2</b>, hovering the mouse over the display reports frequency and amplitudes in the chosen units (<m>freqstyle</m>) to a pop-up display window positioned according to the <m>mousedatapos</m> attribute. <br />
