			</digest>
			<description>
				Syntax: <b>freeze <m>&lt;int: curve&gt;</m> </b><br />				<br />
				The symbol <m>freeze</m> followed by an <m>integer</m> representing curve number (<b>1</b>, <b>2</b>, <b>3</b>, <b>4</b>) will freeze the UI curve of the realtime input at the moment the message is invoked. <br />
